<html><head><meta charset="UTF-8"><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/tips.css"></head><body><p><b>Share profiler reports</b></p><p>IntelliJ Profiler snapshots are saved as files, which enables you to share a performance report with someone else or investigate reports made by others. This is especially convenient, when you want to investigate a problem that is not reproducible in your development environment.</p><p class="image"><img src="images/ij-reveal-snapshot-in-finder.png" alt="Reveal in Finder action in the Recent Snapshots context menu" style="border: 1px solid #55555;" /></p></body></html>